BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 658 Td (Financial expert Suze Orman was once $250,000 in debt and spent years digging) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 643 Td (out. She now teaches millions of women about avoiding the debt traps that keep) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 628 Td (people financially stuck for decades.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F2 12 Tf 72 598 Td (THE LESSON) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 580 Td (Debt means spending money you do not have yet. Credit cards, loans, and) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 566 Td (buy-now-pay-later schemes all create debt. Some debt \(education, home\) can be) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 552 Td (strategic. But consumer debt \(stuff you buy\) is a trap.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 530 Td (How credit cards actually work: you borrow money at 15-25% interest. If you buy) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 516 Td (a $100 item and only pay the minimum each month, you might end up paying $150 or) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 502 Td (more total. The bank profits from your inability to pay in full.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 480 Td (Avoiding debt traps: only buy what you can afford with cash, if you use a credit) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 466 Td (card always pay the FULL balance each month, avoid buy-now-pay-later schemes,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 452 Td (and never borrow money for wants \(only needs if absolutely necessary\).) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 430 Td (The snowball effect of debt: debt leads to stress, which leads to emotional) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 416 Td (spending, which leads to more debt. Breaking this cycle requires awareness,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 402 Td (discipline, and often outside help. Prevention is much easier than cure.) Tj ET

